\id 2TI - Biblica® Open Kiyombe Contemporary New Testament and Psalms 2002 
\h 2 TIMOTE 
\toc1 Nkanda wumuadi wu Polo kuidi Timote 
\toc2 2 Timote 
\toc3 2 Timote 
\mt2 Nkanda wumuadi wu Polo kuidi 
\mt1 Timote 
\c 1  
\s1 Thonono 
\p  
\v 1 Polo, mvuala wu Yesu Klisto mu luzolo lu Nzambi, boso buididi tsila yi luzingu yidi mu Klisto Yesu,  
\v 2 mfidisidi nkanda wawu kuidi Timote muanꞌama wu luzolo. Bika nlemvo, mamboti ayi ndembama bibedi kuidi Nzambi Tata ayi kuidi Klisto Yesu, Pfumu eto, bibanga yaku. 
\s1 Polo wuvutudila Nzambi matondo mu diambu di Timote 
\p  
\v 3 Ndimvutula matondo kuidi Nzambi yoyi ndieta sadila mu mayindu ma ntima wuvedila banga busila bakulu bama ; bila builu ayi muini ndikutebukilanga moyo, mu zithangu zioso mu zindombolo ziama.  
\v 4 Phuila yiwombo yidi yama mu kumona, bu ndieti tebukila matsuela maku moyo, muingi ndibuela mona khini. 
\p  
\v 5 Ndizimbakananga ko minu kikiedika kidi mu ngeyo ; ayi kioki kituama ba mu khayꞌaku yi nketo mama Loyisi ayi mu ngudi aku Ewunise. Tsidi diana ti kidi mu ngeyo. 
\s1 Polo wukindisa Timote mu buela lemisa mbazu 
\p  
\v 6 Diawu ndikutebudila moyo muingi wuluta buela lemisa dikaba di Nzambi didi mu ngeyo ; diodi wutambula bu nditetika mioko miama  
\v 7 bila Nzambi kasia kutuvana Pheve yi boma-boma ko vayi wutuvana pheve yi lulendo, yi luzolo ayi yi diela di kukikebila. 
\p  
\v 8 Diawu kadi mona tsoni mu telama kimbangi mu diambu di Pfumu eto voti mu diambu diama bu ndidi mu nloko mu diambu diandi. Vayi bika wufubakana yama mu ziphasi mu diambu di Nsamu wumboti boso buididi lulendo lu Nzambi.  
\v 9 Bila niandi wutuvukisa ayi wututela mu mbila yinlongo ; bika sia ti boso bubela mavanga meto vayi boso bu bela lukanu luandi veka ayi nlemvo andi wowo katuvana mu Klisto Yesu tuamina thonono yi zithangu.  
\v 10 Vayi buabu wutumonisa wawu bumboti mu ntangu Pfumu eto Yesu Klisto kayiza ; bila niandi wukosikisa lulendo lu lufua, wukienzula luzingu ayi biobi kabifuanga ko mu nzila yi Nsamu Wumbote. 
\p  
\v 11 Mu diambu di Nsamu Wumbo ti beni wawu ndibiekolo nsamuni, mvuala ayi nlongi kuidi Bapakanu.  
\v 12 Ayi diawu ndilembo monina ziphasi ziazi vayi ndikadi mona tsoni mu diambu nzebi mutu wowo ndiwilukila ayi diana tsidi ti lulendo luidi yandi mu keba mambu moso momo ndiyekudulu nate mu lumbu kina. 
\p  
\v 13 Kebanga bumboti mambu ma kiedika momo wuwa kuidi minu mu minu ayi mu luzolo luidi mu Klisto Yesu.  
\v 14 Lundanga bumbote, mu lusadusu lu Pheve Yinlongo mu beto, mambu mambote momo wuyekudulu. 
\s1 Bufula bu Onesifole 
\p  
\v 15 Ngeyo zebi ti batu boso badi mu Azi bandoza, mu bawu muidi Fingele ayi Elimongene.  
\v 16 Bika Pfumu kawokisa mamboti mandi mu nzo yi Onesifole, bila niandi wuba kumbombanga buwombo ayi kasia mona tsoni ko mu diambu di zisieni ziama.  
\v 17 Vayi bu kaba ku Loma, wuthomba mu bufula ayi wumbakula.  
\v 18 Bika Pfumu kamvana diluaku ditambudila mamboti ma Pfumu mu lumbu kina. Ngeyo lutidi zaba phila yoyi katsadisila mu mambu mawombo bu ndiba ku Efeso. 
\c 2  
\s1 Disodi di Klisto 
\p  
\v 1 Diawu ngeyo muanꞌama, bika wukikindisa mu nlemvo wowo widi mu Klisto Yesu.  
\v 2 Mambu momo wuwa kuidi minu va meso ma bambangi bawombo, longa mawu kuidi batu bakuikama bobo babeki bu kumalongila kuidi batu bankaka. 
\p  
\v 3 Bika wumona ziaku ziphasi banga disodi dimboti di Yesu Klisto.  
\v 4 Bila kuisi ko mutu wunkuendanga ku mvita wumbelanga mayindu mu bima bi luzingu lualu mu diambu kamonisa khini mutu wowo wunsonika.  
\v 5 Bobuawu, mutu wunsalanga zitsaka (bipa) kalendi vuiku budu ki ndungunu ko enati kakadi nuana boso buididi mina.  
\v 6 Nkuni zitsola kafueti tuama sala theti tuamina katambula mimbutu.  
\v 7 Sudika bumboti mambu mama thubidi bila niandi veka Pfumu wela kuvana diela mu mambu moso. 
\s1 Kifuani ki Polo 
\p  
\v 8 Tebukilanga Yesu Klisto moyo, wutotukila mu nkuna Davidi, wufuluka mu bafua boso buididi Nsamu wumboti wundieti longa.  
\v 9 Bila mu diambu di Nsamu wumboti beni wawu ndilembo monina ziphasi ayi ndididi wukangama banga mvangi mambimbi. Muaki mambu ma Nzambi masi makangama ko.  
\v 10 Diawu ndilembo kangila ntima mu diambu di batu bobo basobolo muingi bawu mamvawu batambula phulusu yidi mu Yesu Klisto va kimosi ayi nkembo wu kawumani.  
\v 11 Mambu mama madi ma kuikama : 
\q1 Enati tufuidi va kimosi ayi niandi, 
\q1 buna tuela zinga va kimosi ayi niandi. 
\q1  
\v 12 Enati tumvibidila 
\q1 buna tuela yadila va kimosi ayi niandi ; 
\q1 vayi beto kuntunuka, niandi mamvandi wela kututunuka. 
\q1  
\v 13 Enati tuisi ko bakuikama, 
\q1 vayi niandi widi wukuikama, 
\q1 bila niandi veka kalendi kukitunuka ko. 
\s1 Sadila kiedika 
\p  
\v 14 Tebula batu moyo mu mambu momo ; wuba lubula va meso ma Nzambi ti babika ziphaka mu mambu ma phamba makambulu mfunu. Vayi mannatanga ku mbivusu batu bobo banwanga mawu. 
\p  
\v 15 Nuana mu monika va meso ma Nzambi banga mutu wufuana, banga kisadi kikambu mona tsoni ; kinlonga mu busonga mambu ma kiedika. 
\p  
\v 16 Tina ziphaka zi mambu ma phamba ayi makambu dedakana ayi minu bila batu bobo bantubanga mawu beti luta kuendanga mu zithangu zioso ku kambu kinzikanga mambu ma Nzambi  
\v 17 ayi mambu mawu madi banga phuta yindianga nsuni wu nitu. Mu bawu muidi Imene ayi Filete.  
\v 18 Bawu bamana vengama mu kiedika bu beti tubanga ti mfulukulu yimana vioka thama ; balembo zimbisa minu ki batu bankaka.  
\v 19 Muaki fundasio yi ngolo yi Nzambi yidi kaka yitelama ayi yibeki ayi dimbu kiaki : “Pfumu zebi batu bandi, ayi woso mutu weti tangunanga dizina di Pfumu, bika katina mambu mambimbi.” 
\p  
\v 20 Bika sia ti mimvungu mivangulu mu nolo ayi mu palata, ziawu kaka mimmonikanga mu nzo yinneni vayi muidi ayi miomi mivangulu mu minti ayi mu tuma. Miomi mivangulu mu nolo ayi mu palata midi mi luzitu bosi miomi mivangulu mu minti ayi mu tuma miawu minsadulungu kadika lumbu. 
\p  
\v 21 Enati mutu wukikebidi wuvedila mu kambu vanga mambu mama, buna niandi wela kituka mvungu wu luzitu, wunlongo, widi mfunu kuidi vuidi wawu ; wawu widi wukubama mu diambu di mavanga moso mambote. 
\p  
\v 22 Tina zinzinunu zi bumuana vayi tomba busonga, minu, luzolo, ndemama va kimosi ayi batu bobo bansambilanga Pfumu mu ntima wuvedila. 
\p  
\v 23 Tina biuvu bi buvungisi, ayi bikambulu mfunu bila bizabikini ti biawu bieti totula ziphaka.  
\v 24 Bila kisadi ki Pfumu kasi fuana findananga ziphaka ko vayi kafueti ba mutu wulembama kuidi batu boso, mutu widi diela mu longa ayi mu zebi vibidila.  
\v 25 Kafueti teminanga mu malembi batu bobo bankakidilanga bila nani zebi mananga Nzambi lenda kuba vana diela di baludila mavanga ayi tula ku nzayilu yi mambu ma kiedika ;  
\v 26 ayi diela diawu divutukisa mu diambu babaka busionukina mu mintambu mi Satana, wuba kanga mu kuba kuika mu diambu bavanga luzolo luandi. 
\c 3  
\s1 Mambu ma tsisi mu bilumbu bitsuka 
\p  
\v 1 Zaba kuaku ti mu bilumbu bitsuka, muela ba zithangu ziphasi.  
\v 2 Bila batu bela ba buimi, bela ba bakundi ba zimbongo, bela ba luniemo, bela ba lunangu, bela ba mimvuezi mi mambu ma Nzambi, bela ba mitingu kuidi bambuta ziawu, bela zabanga ko vutula matondo, bela zabanga ko ba banlongo ;  
\v 3 bela ba batu bakambulu luzolo, bakambulu kiadi, bela vunina badiawu mambu, bela zabanga ko kukiyala, bela ba batu batsita ; bela ba bambeni zi mamboti.  
\v 4 Bela yekulanga badiawu ; bela vika fuemanga, bela kukinangikanga mu luniemo, bela luta zolanga zikhini viokila Nzambi.  
\v 5 Bela monikanga banga bazebi kinzikanga Nzambi vayi bela tunukanga mambu momo mammonisanga zingolo zi mambu ma Nzambi. Bika wutatukila batu ba phila yoyi.  
\v 6 Bankaka mu bawu bankotanga mu zinzo ; ayi bambuilanga baketo bakambulu mayindu masikama, ayi bannatanga zitu ki masumu momo bavola ayi bammonanga tsatu yi mambu mambimbi ma phila mu phila.  
\v 7 Baketo beti longukanga mu zithangu zioso vayi balendi baka bu tudila ku nzayilu yi mambu ma kiedika ko.  
\v 8 Banga Yanesi ayi Yambelesi bamanga wilukila Moyize, buawu bobo batu beni bamengi wilukila kiedika ; bu badi batu babivusu mu diela diawu ayi minu kiawu kizimbalanga bu kieti toto.  
\v 9 Balendi kuenda ku ntuala ko bila buvungisi buawu buela monika kuidi batu boso, banga bubela batu ba buadi bobo. 
\s1 Kangama mu mambu momo wulonguka 
\p  
\v 10 Vayi kuidi ngeyo, wulandikini malongi mama, khadulu ama, zikhanu ziama, minu kiama ; lembama kuama luzolo luama ayi mvibudulu ama.  
\v 11 Ngeyo wumona zinzomono ziama ayi ziphasi ziama, phila zimbuidila ku Antioshe, ku Ikone, ku Lisitele. Ayi phila zinzomono mbi ndikambu mona ! Vayi Pfumu wukhula mu zizioso.  
\v 12 Muaki zaba ti babo bobo batidi zinga luzingu luvedila va meso ma Nzambi, mu lusadulu lu Yesu Klisto, bela zomo.  
\v 13 Vayi batu bambimbi ayi bankua luvunu bela luta vanganga mambu mambimbi ; bela vuna bankaka ayi bawu veka bavunuka.  
\v 14 Vayi ngeyo, kangama mu mambu momo wulonguka ayi momo mazabikini ti madi makuikama bu zebi mutu wulonga mawu.  
\v 15 Tona mu kimuana kiaku, ngeyo zebi Masonuku Manlongo ; mawu malenda kuvana diela di kiedika mu diambu wubaka phulusu mu minu mu Klisto Yesu.  
\v 16 Masonuku mamo masonimina mu lulendo lu Nzambi, madi mfunu mu longa, mu tubidila, mu ludika ayi longa mu diatila mu busonga,  
\v 17 muingi mutu wu Nzambi kaba wuduka ayi kaba wukubama mu vanga mavanga moso mamboti. 
\c 4  
\s1 Longa mambu ma Nzambi 
\p  
\v 1 Minu ndikutumina va meso ma Nzambi ayi ma Yesu Klisto wela sambisa batu banzinga ayi bafua, mu diambu di bu kela monika ayi mu diambu di Kipfumu kiandi ti  
\v 2 longa mambu ma Nzambi ayi longa mawu mu bufula mu zithangu zioso, yiba yifuana voti yikambu fuana. Totula luvunu lu batu, temina ayi lubula mu mvibusulu yingolo ayi lubula mu ndongolo.  
\v 3 Bila thangu yidi yela ba ti batu bakadi buela zola wa malongi ma kiedika ; vayi mu diambu di zitsatu ziawu bela kukivangila minlongi miwombo-wombo, miomi miela kuba kamba mambu momo makutu mawu matidi wa.  
\v 4 Bela kanga matu mawu mu diambu babika buela wa mambu ma kiedika vayi bela zibula mawu mu diambu di wa zinongo.  
\v 5 Vayi ngeyo, wukikeba mu mambu moso momo ; vibidila mu ziphasi, sala kisalu kiaku ki kinsamuni ayi manisa kisalu bumboti. 
\s1 Polo manisini kisalu kiandi 
\p  
\v 6 Bila mu diambu diama ndidi wukubama mu tambuku banga dikaba ayi thangu yi kuendila yizidi.  
\v 7 Minu ndinueni nduanunu yimboti, ndinakuni zithinu nate kuna tsuka ; ndikebidi minu.  
\v 8 Buabu nzebi ti ndilundulu budu ki kipfumu ki busonga, kioki Pfumu, zuzi disonga, kela kuphana mu lumbu kina. Bika sia ti kuidi minu kaka vayi wela kivana kuidi baboso bobo banvingilanga mbonokono andi mu luzolo. 
\s1 Zitsangu zi tsuka zi Polo 
\p  
\v 9 Sia nsualu mu vika kuiza ku ndidi.  
\v 10 Bila Demasi wundiefudi ; bu kavukumunkini mu landakana nza yayi ayi wuyenda kuandi ku Tesalonika. Kelesensi wuyenda ku Ngalatiya ayi Tite niandi wuyenda ku Dalimati.  
\v 11 Luka kaka widi yama vava. Bu wu nkuiza vitula Malako, kiza yaku bila mfunu ndimvuidi mu kisalu kiama.  
\v 12 Ndituma Titsike ku Efeso.  
\v 13 Bu wunkuiza, buna wundatina yunga ki ndibika mu nzo Kalipusi ku Tolowasi ayi zibuku, buidi ziozi zivangimina mu minkanda mi bibulu.  
\v 14 Alekisandele, dimfulanga bisengo, wuphangila mambimbi mawombo. Vayi Pfumu wela kumvutudila boso buididi mavanga mandi.  
\v 15 Mamvaku wukikeba mu diambu diandi, bila niandi wukakidila mu kingolo mambu meto.  
\v 16 Bu ndisamba mu khumbu yi thete, kadi mutu kasia kutsadisa ko ; babo bathina. Vayi bika babika kuba tangila nzimbala yoyi.  
\v 17 Pfumu niandi wutelama va ndambu va ndiba ayi wukhindisa mu diambu di mu minu ndongolo yiba yiduka ayi yidukila mu makanda moso nate kuidi Bapakanu. Bukiedika minu ndikulu mu munu wu khosi.  
\v 18 Nzebi ti Pfumu wela kukhula mu mavanga mamo mambimbi ayi wela kukheba mu diambu di mu Kipfumu kiandi ku Diyilu. Bika nkembo wubanga yandi mu zithangu zioso. Amen. 
\s1 Zimboti 
\p  
\v 19 Vana mboti kuidi Pilisika ayi Akilasi ayi nzo yoso yi Onesifole.  
\v 20 Elasite wusiala ku Kolinto ; mu kimbevo ndibika Tolofime ku Mile.  
\v 21 Tomba bu kuizila tuamina sivu. Ewubulusi, Pudensi, Linusi, Klodia ayi bakhomba zioso zifidisidi mboti.  
\v 22 Bika Pfumu kabanga mu Pheve aku. Nlemvo wubanga yaku.